## 🎯 Project Objective

Build an **interactive sales dashboard** that helps business stakeholders:
- Track sales performance across branches
- Identify top-selling product categories
- Understand customer behavior patterns
- Monitor KPIs in real-time
- Make data-driven business decisions

---

## 📈 Dashboard Features

### 1️⃣ Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)
| KPI | Value |
|-----|-------|
| **Total Revenue** | $322,966 |
| **Total Profit** | $15,379 |
| **Average Transaction** | $307 |
| **Average Rating** | 6.97 / 10 |
| **Total Transactions** | 1,000+ |

### 2️⃣ 7 Interactive Charts

| # | Chart Type | Purpose |
|---|------------|---------|
| 1 | **Bar Chart** | Revenue by Product Line |
| 2 | **Line Chart** | Monthly Sales Trend |
| 3 | **Bar Chart** | Sales by City/Branch |
| 4 | **Donut Chart** | Customer Type Breakdown |
| 5 | **Pie Chart** | Payment Method Distribution |
| 6 | **Stacked Bar** | Gender vs. Product Line |
| 7 | **Scatter Plot** | Rating Analysis |

### 3️⃣ Interactive Features
- **Slicers** for filtering by date, city, and product
- **Dynamic charts** that update with filters
- **KPI cards** showing real-time metrics
- **Mobile responsive** design

