## 💡 Key Business Insights

### 1. Revenue Leaders
- **Food & Beverages** generates highest revenue (**$56,144**)
- **Electronic Accessories** is most profitable
- All categories perform similarly ($52K-$56K)

### 2. Customer Behavior
- **Members** contribute **52%** of total revenue
- Members spend **13% more** per transaction ($326 vs $288)
- **E-wallet** is preferred payment (42%)

### 3. Geographic Performance
- **Naypyitaw** slightly outperforms ($110,000+)
- All 3 cities show balanced performance

### 4. Operational Insights
- **Peak Hours:** 10:00 AM - 2:00 PM
- **Best Month:** March (15% growth)

